        "_account_id": 192,
        "name": "Brian Behlendorf",
        "email": "behlendorf1@llnl.gov",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2013-09-25 16:49:43.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nIt turns out that the udmu_objset_name_get(), udmu_userprop_set_str(), and udmu_userprop_get_str() functions are never used by the zfs osd.  This is all dead code, and I'd rather not add any autoconf checks for dead code.\n\nI propose we just remove it.  This has the additional advantage of further whittling away at udmu.c which I would very much like to see entirely removed at some point.\n\nPatch to follow shortly.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
